{"word":"G5595 - ψωμίζω - psōmízō - pso-mid'-zo - Feed","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ψωμίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">psōmízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pso-mid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Feed</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - போஜனங்கொடு, அன்னதானம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to feed by putting a bit or crumb (of food) into the mouth, to feed, nourish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G5596 - ψωμίον - psōmíon - pso-mee'-on/5596\">G5596</a>; to <i>supply</i> with <i>bits</i>, that is, (genitive case) to <i>nourish:</i> - (bestow to) feed.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}